Stephen Szabo: Germany does not support what Israelis have done in Gaza.
However, because of the special relationship between the country and Israel, Germany must be careful.
But at the same time, I don't think it supports the American position either.
Germany wanted to demonstrate its independence without being overly critical of Israel.
